timeline.bodyText:
you are checking whether it is set in order to enable the read/write/execute bits, but this won't remove any bits that are already set by the umask when the file was created.
I think you need to do
f.setReadable(permissions.isOwnerRead(), true);
f.setReadable(permissions.isOtherRead(), false);
f.setWritable(permissions.isOwnerWrite(), true);
f.setWritable(permissions.isOtherWrite(), false);
f.setExecutable(permissions.isOwnerExecute(), true);
f.setExecutable(permissions.isOtherExecute(), false);

